title: #92Noon! Boudreau, Baseball, Birk & Brett!
description: Bruce Boudreau starts the show! Then Aaron Gleeman is in studio to break down the Twins kicking off the season tomorrow, then the Birk bit is in studio for a couple segments. SCSU Hockey coach Brett Larson closes #92Noon, as his team is the top seed in the NCAA tourney.
